name: Cube Collector (John Lynch)
description:
This is a simple puzzle game where the player must guide 4 cubes out the back door of the level to win the game.

-Music and sound effects were provided by Patrick Shufelt. 

-Producer was Sam Burke.

-Vadim Mayorskiy and K. "Ezy" Vazque created 3D assets.

-Ryan Normand and John Lynch were the programmers.
